          <title>England gets back to winning ways but interim coach Carsley says team needs a 'world class' manager</title>
          <description><![CDATA[After three wins from four games as England interim coach, Lee Carsley appeared to distance himself from taking on the job full time. A 3-1 victory against Finland in the Nations League on Sunday saw England get back to winning ways after the shock 2-1 home loss to Greece.]]></description>
